{"id":634385,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【网络民议】微信再现大规模封号/","date":"2020-02-05T20:31:49Z","modified":"2020-02-06T08:07:33Z","title":"【网络民议】微信再现大规模封号","content":"<p>CDT编者按：近几日微信以“传播恶意谣言”为由大规模封号，导致很多受害用户聚集在微博上诉苦喊冤。他们创建了一个“微信封号”的超话，里面有近四百个帖子，很多人讲述了最近自己在突然被封号后的惨重损失，他们丢失了七八年来大量生活记录和工作、生活中累积的人脉，在疫情期间无法正常得知消息，生活十分不便，这使得不少人陷入了悲伤、愤怒和抑郁的情绪中。本超话一度登上超话社会类话题榜首，但截至目前为止，微博平台上的“微信封号”超话话题已经被删除。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634412\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话-300x103.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"172\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话-300x103.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话-1024x353.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话-768x265.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话-1080x372.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号超话.png 1474w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634396\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4-300x101.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4-300x101.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4-1024x345.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4-768x259.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4-1080x364.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号2-4.png 1194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634411\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号17-300x115.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号17-300x115.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号17-1024x391.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/封号17-768